quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,"Toto Abasuubili bamala okhubura."
  23,2,"Balia abehotselesinjia mukhulaama (mukhuswaliya) khwabu."
  23,3,"Nende balia aberetsanga ehale nende amakhuwa kabulamwo oluchendo."
  23,4,"Nende balia abarusinjia eshihanwa shia Izakaa."
  23,5,"Nende balia abalindanga ebiekenyi biabu."
  23,6,"Halali khubakhasi babu nohomba balia abemikhono chiabu emilunji chiatila, kho abo shibafunanibwa tawe."
  23,7,"Ne ulia wenya kalali kano tawe, abo nibo babura eshichelo."
  23,8,"Nende balia bahenganga ebiabachelekhwa nende indakano yabu."
  23,9,"Nende balia balumiililanga khumalaamo kabu (iswala)."
  23,10,"Abo nibo balichelama (balibukula)."
  23,11,"Nibo abalichelama Firdaus mwikulu, balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsioosi."
  23,12,"Ne toto khwaloonga Omundu okhurulana nende liloba."
  23,13,"Mana nikhumulonga okhurulana nende amatsi kolwibulo, akarebwa habundu ehenzefu muno."
  23,14,"Mana nikhukalonga okhuba lilika, mana nikhulonga lilika okhuba eshitonye shieyinyama, mana nikhulonga eshitonye shieyinyama okhubamwo ebikumba, mana nikhufunikha ebikumba inyama, mana nikhumukhola okhuba eshilonje shindi. Ni woluyali muno Nyasaye, Omulonji omulayi muno umalayo."
  23,15,"Mana toto enywe olunyuma lwa ako mulifwa."
  23,16,"Mana toto enywe mulilamusibwa inyanga yeyindukho."
  23,17,"Ne toto khwalonga hekulu wenyu tsinjila saba, ne efwe shikhwali abebilila eshilonje shiosishiosi tawe."